HEADWORD: Cheap-john
<hw>Cheap"-john`</hw>
<pr>(?)</pr>, }</mhw> <pos>n.</pos> <def>A seller of low-priced, shoddy,
or second goods; a hawker.</def>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> huckster, hawker, tout.</syn>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

